                            <h5 style="font-weight: 800;"><i>Select that which resonates with you :</i></h5>
                            <div class="mt-4 inline" style="font-weight: 800;">
                                <input id="one" name="rep1" type="checkbox"
                                    value="Frequent use of emergency dates may lead to your account being frozen. Tread carefully, lest you find yourself locked out.">
