                                    value="You have made several incorrect bus requests to the admin.Please ensure their accuracy before sending. If you are found to be deceitful,your account will be removed.">
                                <label for="" class="ml-2">You have made several incorrect bus requests to the admin.
                                    Please ensure their accuracy before sending. If you are found to be deceitful, <br>
                                    your
                                    account will be removed.</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-4 inline" style="font-weight: 800;">
                                <input name="rep3" id="one" type="checkbox"
                                    value="We have detected malicious activity on your account. Should this happen again, your account will be banned, and we will proceed with legal action under the Indian IT Act.">
                                <label for="" class="ml-2">We have detected malicious activity on your account. Should
                                    this happen again, your account will be banned, and we will proceed with legal
                                    action <br> under the Indian IT Act.</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-4 inline" style="font-weight: 800;">
                                <input name="rep3" id="two" type="checkbox"
                                    value="We have received numerous complaints from our passengers.Remember, customers are our top priority. Should any more complaints arise,we will be compelled to take action against you.">
